HEADWORD: Nevermore
<hw>Nev"er*more`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Never again; at
no time hereafter.</def> <rj><au>Testament of Love.
Tyndale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Where springtime of the Hesperides⟦br⟧
Begins, but endeth <qex>nevermore</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Longfellow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>never-say-die</ent>⟦br⟧
